label: Gost Zvuk
description:
Pacy, Chain Reaction-style dub techno, hopping acid and skronky electro from Moscow’s Flaty

Tilting in with the skidding 140bpm+ dub techno of ‘Graf Ruin’, he bugs the ‘floor with a mean dose of uptempo, mercurial acid in ‘Hornets’, and brings it back down to Skam-like electro with ‘Rn’.
